 ability to work in different basins is very exciting as a geologist” – clayton schultz sm energy geologist “the personal development and technical opportunities at sm energy provide one of the best foundations for building a career in oil and gas  sm’s commitment to their employees is evident in their early career development program which attracted me to the company” – ritthy son sm energy engineer “from my first day at sm energy i have been challenged with projects and roles typically held by seasoned professionals yet the entire time i have been given the necessary support framework to succeed learn and grow in my career at a very fast pace” – cade campbell senior landman “sm energy has given me responsibility and a sense of purpose from day one with meaningful tasks that impact the business ownership of my projects and support from experienced professionals” – meghan tonello technical development supervisor sm energy is an equal opportunity employer and in accordance with applicable federal and state laws will not discriminate in recruitment employment promotion training or any other jobrelated matters regardless of race religion color sex sexual orientation gender identity genetic information national origin age disability military or veteran status or any other classification proscribed under applicable federal state or local law if a disabled applicant needs assistance please call  home about us oil and gas exploration operations land relations investor relationscommunity careers career opportunities college recruiting talent development corporate responsibility look beyondcontact us contacts sherman st ste denver co   site map our operations land relations investor relations community careers corporate responsibility extra links about us contact us company news socials facebook linkedin youtube twitter